  "title": "Customer Service Coordinator (Warehouse / West)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Handle incoming phone calls from customers and direct them to the appropriate personnel.</li>\n  <li>Assist in preparing and compiling regular reports as scheduled.</li>\n  <li>Organize and maintain an efficient filing system for records and documents.</li>\n  <li>Update and oversee the implementation of office policies and procedures.</li>\n  <li>Manage office supply inventory, including placing orders and sourcing competitive deals and suppliers.</li>\n  <li>Serve as the primary point of contact for both internal teams and external clients.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with executive and senior administrative assistants to address inquiries and support requests from senior management.</li>\n  <li>Arrange and manage import/export shipments and related logistics.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
